author: bryanduxbury
msg: THRIFT-511. rb: Better performing hash method for generated structs
This patch uses a hash function that takes into account the hashes of struct elements, instead of just returning 0. This make hashes of Thrift structs O(1) instead of O(n).

msg: THRIFT-489. java: Java enum validation only validates explicitly assigned values
